-- Bain Plans China-Focused Fund of Up to $2.5 Billion, Financial Times Says
-- Vivek Shankar
-- 2010-07-12T23:44:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/bain-plans-china-focused-fund-of-up-to-2-5-billion-financial-times-says.html

          
          
             Bain Capital LLC plans a new $2
billion to $2.5 billion China-focused fund, the Financial Times
reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the matter.  
          
          


  


        